  <h1 class="caption">We want to hear what you have to say</h1>
  <h3>Express yourself, ask a question, request an appointment for personalized pieces.</h3>
  <div class="row padding-top">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
    <div class="" id="map"></div>
    </div>
